  "dialogue": {
    "title": "Unlucky Day",
    "lines": [
      {"speaker": "角色", "chinese": "我们一大早就��发了。天儿不错,我们一路吹着风,心里别提多美了。", "pinyin": "Wǒmen yì dà zǎo jiù chūfā le. Tiān'er búcuò, wǒmen yì lù chuīzhe fēng, xīnli biéti duō měi le.", "english": "We left early. The weather was nice, the wind blowing as we went, I felt great."},
      {"speaker": "角色", "chinese": "可是车走着走着,突然抛锚了。", "pinyin": "Kěshi chē zǒuzhe zǒuzhe, túrán pãomão le.", "english": "But suddenly the car broke down."},
      {"speaker": "角色", "chinese": "他的车以前从来没出过毛病,偏偏今天坏了。", "pinyin": "Tā de chē yǐqian cónglái méi chūguo máobìng, pianpian jīntiān huàile.", "english": "His car never had problems before, but today it broke down."},
      {"speaker": "角色", "chinese": "我们费了九牛二虎之力把车推到了修车店。", "pinyin": "Wǒmen fèile jiŭ niú èr hủ zhĩ lì ba chē tuī dàole xiū chē diàn.", "english": "With tremendous effort, we pushed the car to the repair shop."},
      {"speaker": "角色", "chinese": "今天真是祸不单行。我想可能是因为我逃课,老天要惩罚我。", "pinyin": "Jīntiān zhënshi huò búdān xíng. Wǒ xiǎng kěnéng shì yīnwèi wǒ táo kè, lǎotiān yào chéngfá wǒ.", "english": "Today was full of troubles. I think it's because I skipped class, and heaven is punishing me."}
    ]
  },
